{
  "id": "5deb5b2e75e33000178f38a7",
  "title": "変更凍結",
  "created": 1575705393,
  "updated": 1575706172,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5deb5b2e75e33000178f38a7",
      "text": "変更凍結",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705393,
      "updated": 1575705393
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5b7baff09e000049c6d5",
      "text": "今のRegroupの仕組み",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705467,
      "updated": 1575705472
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5b31aff09e000049c6cf",
      "text": "\tURLを知らなければ閲覧できない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705394,
      "updated": 1575705427
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5b54aff09e000049c6d1",
      "text": "\t\t→閲覧用URLを知っている＝閲覧権限がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705428,
      "updated": 1575705441
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5b60aff09e000049c6d2",
      "text": "\t編集用URLを別途発行する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705441,
      "updated": 1575705448
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5b68aff09e000049c6d3",
      "text": "\t\t→編集用URLを知っている＝編集権限がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705448,
      "updated": 1575705464
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5b77aff09e000049c6d4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705464,
      "updated": 1575705474
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5b81aff09e000049c6d6",
      "text": "これは[Google Docs]などと同じ仕組み",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705474,
      "updated": 1575705519
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5baeaff09e000049c6d9",
      "text": "[Scrapbox]を使い始めた人がよく口に出すニーズでもある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705519,
      "updated": 1575706172
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5bbcaff09e000049c6da",
      "text": "\t例",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705533,
      "updated": 1575705807
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5cceaff09e000049c6df",
      "text": "\t\t「privateプロジェクトの中の1ページだけ、他の人に見せられないか？」→できません",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705807,
      "updated": 1575705807
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5bccaff09e000049c6db",
      "text": "\t\t「publicプロジェクトの中の1ページだけ、他の人に編集権限を渡せないか？」→できません",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705549,
      "updated": 1575705808
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5bf5aff09e000049c6dc",
      "text": "\tScrapboxはプロジェクト内でのリンクに重きを置いている設計思想なのだろう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705590,
      "updated": 1575705658
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5c39aff09e000049c6dd",
      "text": "パラレルワークが盛んになって行く流れの中で、全ドキュメントのアクセス権が「プロジェクトのメンバーかどうか」を密結合になってる設計はだんだん使いづらくなって行くだろう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705658,
      "updated": 1575705801
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5cc8aff09e000049c6de",
      "text": "\t例",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705801,
      "updated": 1575705803
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5cd1aff09e000049c6e0",
      "text": "\t\t[Slackのシングルチャンネルゲスト]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705810,
      "updated": 1575705822
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5cd7aff09e000049c6e1",
      "text": "\t\t[kintoneのゲストスペース]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705815,
      "updated": 1575705826
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5ba8aff09e000049c6d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705512,
      "updated": 1575705512
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5b83aff09e000049c6d7",
      "text": "「URLを知っているかどうか」というカジュアルなアクセス権制御",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705475,
      "updated": 1575705884
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5d1caff09e000049c6e3",
      "text": "\t「閲覧」と「編集」だけではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705884,
      "updated": 1575705895
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5d27aff09e000049c6e4",
      "text": "\t例えば編集権限を持った人が複数いる状態で編集合戦が起こったら？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705895,
      "updated": 1575705912
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5d38aff09e000049c6e5",
      "text": "\t\t→Wikipediaの場合、「保護」が行われる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705912,
      "updated": 1575706071
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5d00aff09e000049c6e2",
      "text": "\t\t\t[Wikipedia:編集合戦 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E7%B7%A8%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E6%88%A6]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575705856,
      "updated": 1575706083
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5de3aff09e000049c6e7",
      "text": "\t\t\t[Wikipedia:保護依頼 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E4%BE%9D%E9%A0%BC]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575706083,
      "updated": 1575706093
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5de2aff09e000049c6e6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575706083,
      "updated": 1575706083
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5defaff09e000049c6e8",
      "text": "というわけで編集を停止する権限があってもいいな、と思った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575706097,
      "updated": 1575706132
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5e12aff09e000049c6ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575706130,
      "updated": 1575706130
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5e12aff09e000049c6eb",
      "text": "優先度は低い、少なくとも複数人が編集するRegroup Mapが出現するまでは必要ない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575706130,
      "updated": 1575706155
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5e2aaff09e000049c6ec",
      "text": "[pRegroup2020]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575706155,
      "updated": 1609757747
    },
    {
      "id": "5deb5df1aff09e000049c6e9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575706097,
      "updated": 1575706097
    }
  ]
}